==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: -escent
<hw>-es"cent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[From the ending
<ets>-escens</ets>, <ets>-entis</ets>, of the p. pr. of inchoative verbs
in Latin.]</ety> <def>A suffix signifying <xex>beginning</xex>,
<xex>beginning to be</xex>; <as>as, adol<ex>escent</ex>,
efferv<ex>escent</ex>, etc.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Eschalot</ent>⟦br⟧
